flowchart TD
    U[Authorized Viewer Device] --> ZT[Private Zero Trust / VPN / Identity-Aware Proxy]
    P[Phone Camera Source] --> ZT
    ZT --> RP[Reverse Proxy: TLS, Headers, Rate Limits]
    RP --> FE[Frontend Static Web App]
    FE --> API[Backend API: Identity Validation, RBAC, Token Broker]
    API --> DB[(PostgreSQL: Users, Grants, Sessions, Audit)]
    API --> LK[LiveKit WebRTC SFU]
    P --> LK
    LK --> U
    API --> AUD[Hash-Chained Audit Events]

    subgraph Future Camera Network
        IPCAM[IP Camera / NVR / ONVIF / RTSP]
        VLAN[Dedicated Camera VLAN]
        RELAY[RTSP/ONVIF Ingest Relay]
        IPCAM --> VLAN --> RELAY --> LK
    end

    ATT[Unknown Visitor / Bot / Scanner] -. blocked/no route .-> ZT
    ATT -. no public origin .-> RP
